    • addImagePathPlaceholders

      public void addImagePathPlaceholders(String[] imagePathPlaceholders)
      Part 3 of "counter hack for a hack" initialized in Javascript file eform_floating_toolbar.js This method fetches image paths stored in hidden fields and restores them into empty image src values. Empty image src values are the result of using Javascript in the eForm to dynamically set paths for images.
